description:
Listen to Hayes Carll talk about one of the weirdest gigs he's played
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Hayes Carll has played a lot of gigs in his career — and in this interview with Bill DeVille in The Current studio, Hayes shares the story of one of his weirdest gigs ever.

description:
Watch Dessa perform "Tough Call" in studio
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Minneapolis multi-hyphenate artist Dessa visited The Current to play a pair of new songs for 2025 — "Camelot" and "Tough Call" — and a song from her 2023 album, "Bury The Lede. Watch a performance of "Tough Call" above.
